Package org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.itinfrastructure.server

Class ITAssetRESTService

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.itinfrastructure.server.ITAssetRESTService
public class ITAssetRESTService extends Object
ITAssetRESTService is the server-side of ExternalSourceClientBase. It is called from the specific clients that manage the specializations of IT Infrastructure assets.
